{"tid":1361324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無盲撐左達哥一個月既兄弟開始後悔了？","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T03:06:07.000Z","uid":5649,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"66be62e97f6cb7bfa36f9496149a9d3bb1c8be8a","tid":1361324,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"依一個月我不停幫達哥辯護<br />\n論點唔多講<br />\n但我只係以為佢為錢唔發聲，內心係撐反送中的<br />\n點知今日條片我先醒<br />\n原來佢一直無關心過香港問題，佢只係關心佢自己同兄弟個達朝<br />\n唉，我唔知講咩好<br />\n人生失去一樣好重要既野既感覺<br />\n。"},{"pid":"d3c963fa290f2a51f5f20df63d1c30de78a40dad","tid":1361324,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"8cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c217538ffba2d0a75f4dde73eb6452b9c43762af","tid":1361324,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c963fa290f2a51f5f20df63d1c30de78a40dad","tid":1361324,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"8cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"============================"},{"pid":"6a6cfa8a89e820c8f4b2ddf0eeb3085586b2fddd","tid":1361324,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"達哥咁緊張錢都肯買禮物送俾兄弟<br />\n原諒牠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0228f62394b3acaf48fd917663ab368e7d668a82","tid":1361324,"uid":206382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ytWUKP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ytWUKP.png&h=66439494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3263885ec2fa30934af7dc5bcfa39550675ab90c","tid":1361324,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a6cfa8a89e820c8f4b2ddf0eeb3085586b